  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "You have two ways of accessing the HRE in Hardhat: implicitly (from `global`), or explicitly (importing it / as a task param).\r\n\r\nOur documentation is very inconsistent about this, and it can lead to confusion to users, and to PRs like #1753 or [this one](https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/pull/1554/files/8e6b5a28a626e565005a6f5fa119f710da8fb715#diff-c7a9d3c75c761cf681a348c30f37922ae7eea091e634f465a1a8d789d8a5020f) that increase the inconsistency even further.\r\n\r\nWe should come up with a unified way of explaining this (e.g. always access things implicitly), apply it everywhere, and create a section in the documentation explaining each way of doing things and their limitations..",
